Pro Tools

Tools that help you watch stocks, track your holdings and decide what to do next.

My Portfolio

Get detailed information on your holdings with My Portfolio by securely syncing your brokerage accounts with Plaid. Review personalized news, events calendar, beta composition, movers, and detailed holdings.

Link My Portfolio

Stocks Screener

Stocks Screener

Find relevant stocks based on your investment strategies using market, fundamental, financial, and technical attributes. Save and come back to your screens any time. Find the stock screener in the Pro dropdown of the CNBC menu.

Watchlist

Watch stocks of interest and get alerts with custom watchlists. Explore industry trends with premade lists or create your own.

Customize your Markets Banner

Click the add symbol to create a custom market banner with the securities, indicators, and benchmarks you want to reference most throughout the site. Add the symbols you want to track, and see the latest price movements for the stocks that matter most to you.
